I identified a targeted gap: trailing punctuation is only emitted as positive evidence, so citations without trailing punctuation produce no explicit `false/0` slots. I’m patching both decompiler and triple projection to emit explicit trailing-punct booleans/counts (and punct kind when present), then I’ll extend the slot regression tests accordingly.
